details.text:
This section contains a summary of the area and f<sub>MAX</sub> data generated by compiling the components through Quartus. 
To generate the data, run a Quartus compile on the project created for this design. To run the Quartus compile:
  1) Change to the quartus directory (./myproject-fpga.prj/quartus)
  2) quartus_sh --flow compile quartus_compile

children.name: Run Quartus compile to populate this section. See details for more information.
